The goal is `Prod.fst (prover.runWithLog ...) = prover.run ...`
After `simp [runWithLog]`, Lean will expand `prover.runWithLog` to its definition:
`Prod.fst ((simQ loggingOracle (prover.run ...)).run) = prover.run ...`

The definition of `simQ` is `(fun {α β} [Oracles α] [Oracles β] [OracleReduction α β] (f : α → β) => ...)`
